{
  "stem": "3658.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We each told each other stories, just trying to keep the spirit up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this guy, the one that was cutting the bread, he was talking what a good chef he was, [LAUGHS] and what he used to cook.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You can imagine the things that one remembers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we stayed there for quite a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how many weeks there was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It could have been-- it was in April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it wouldn't have been more than four or five weeks, maybe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Maybe a bit more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember, exactly, a time or dates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We just didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then one day, it was Friday-- that date I do remember-- Friday, the 4th of May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A Jeep drove in, an American Jeep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And people started to-- we couldn't-- we were already that weak, that we had to hold each other to get up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You can imagine how we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it's-- and an American Jeep came into the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody says, American Jeep and American-- you know, American soldier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one Jeep just that drove in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw the Germans throwing down their guns from the-- that surrounded us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that was the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was-- they had petrol all around the camp, surrounded, just to burn us all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whether they waited for more people to come in or what to do the job in one hit, or before the Americans come in to the last minute.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was just luck that he just drove in from-- apparently from the main road.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He saw there was some-- some little road there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he drove in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he discovered the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they didn't know how many people--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were coming with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
